# NOTE: do NOT ignore erp-app/ here. The erp-aqobah Vercel project builds from
# erp-app/ as its Root Directory; a root-level ignore of it discards the app
# source and breaks that build. landing-aqobah serves only the root index.html,
# so the extra erp-app/ files it uploads are harmless.
